    "syntax_rules": "### 核心约束\n- **堆叠模式**: 多系列建议使用 stack: true 以展示总量贡献。\n- **数据容器**: 必须使用 data: [{ values: [...] }] 数组包装。\n### 基础语法\n```dsl\nTitle: 示例标题\nSpec: { \"type\": \"area\", \"xField\": \"x\", \"yField\": \"y\", \"stack\": true, \"data\": [...] }\n```",
    "official_example": "Title: 能源消耗结构分析\nColorPalette: forest\nShowLabel: true\n\nSpec: {\n  \"type\": \"area\",\n  \"data\": [{ \"values\": [\n    {\"x\":\"周一\",\"y\":50,\"c\":\"电\"}, {\"x\":\"周一\",\"y\":30,\"c\":\"气\"},\n    {\"x\":\"周二\",\"y\":55,\"c\":\"电\"}, {\"x\":\"周二\",\"y\":35,\"c\":\"气\"}\n  ]}],\n  \"xField\": \"x\", \"yField\": \"y\", \"seriesField\": \"c\", \"stack\": true,\n  \"label\": { \"visible\": true },\n  \"axes\": [{ \"orient\": \"bottom\" }, { \"orient\": \"left\" }],\n  \"legends\": [{ \"visible\": true, \"orient\": \"bottom\" }]\n}",
