    "syntax_rules": "### 核心约束\n- **轴线规范**: 必须显式包含 orient: \"bottom\" 和 \"left\" 两个轴配置。\n- **数据容器**: 必须使用 data: [{ values: [...] }] 数组包装。\n### 基础语法\n```dsl\nTitle: 标题\nSpec: { \"type\": \"scatter\", \"xField\": \"x\", \"yField\": \"y\", \"data\": [...] }\n```",
    "official_example": "Title: 温度与压力相关性相关性分析\nColorPalette: tech\nShowTitle: true\n\nSpec: {\n  \"type\": \"scatter\",\n  \"data\": [{ \"values\": [\n    {\"x\":200,\"y\":10.2,\"c\":\"批次A\"}, {\"x\":210,\"y\":11.5,\"c\":\"批次A\"},\n    {\"x\":205,\"y\":10.8,\"c\":\"批次B\"}, {\"x\":215,\"y\":11.2,\"c\":\"批次B\"}\n  ]}],\n  \"xField\": \"x\", \"yField\": \"y\", \"seriesField\": \"c\",\n  \"axes\": [\n    { \"orient\": \"bottom\", \"title\": {\"visible\": true, \"text\": \"温度 (°C)\"} },\n    { \"orient\": \"left\", \"title\": {\"visible\": true, \"text\": \"压力 (MPa)\"} }\n  ],\n  \"legends\": [{ \"visible\": true, \"orient\": \"bottom\" }]\n}",
