    "expert_logic": "### 变动归因分析 (Waterfall Chart)\n用于展示从起始值到结束值的各因素增减贡献分析。\n- **汇总约束**: 必须显式标记总计项，并匹配 `total` 配置。",
    "syntax_rules": "### 核心约束\n- **汇总标注**: 最终项必须在 `values` 中显式标记 `\"isTotal\": true`。\n- **追踪字段**: `Spec` 必须包含 `total: { \"tagField\": \"isTotal\" }` 配置。\n- **轴线规范**: 必须显式包含 `bottom` 和 `left` 轴。\n### 基础语法\n```dsl\nSpec: { \"type\": \"waterfall\", \"xField\": \"x\", \"yField\": \"y\", \"total\": {\"tagField\":\"isTotal\"}, \"data\": [...] }\n```",
    "official_example": "Title: 质量成本变动归因分析\nColorPalette: vibrant\n\nSpec: {\n  \"type\": \"waterfall\",\n  \"data\": [{\n    \"values\": [\n      { \"x\": \"起始成本\", \"y\": 1000 },\n      { \"x\": \"材料波动\", \"y\": 200 },\n      { \"x\": \"最终成本\", \"y\": 1200, \"isTotal\": true }\n    ]\n  }],\n  \"xField\": \"x\", \"yField\": \"y\",\n  \"total\": { \"tagField\": \"isTotal\" },\n  \"label\": { \"visible\": true },\n  \"axes\": [\n    { \"orient\": \"bottom\", \"label\": { \"visible\": true } },\n    { \"orient\": \"left\", \"label\": { \"visible\": true } }\n  ]\n}",
    "input_schema": {
      "prompt": {
